@startuml BlindReview_Deployment_Architecture
title BlindReview — deployment architecture\n(PR → **staging** / preview · merge to **main** → **production**)

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Verdana
skinparam noteFontSize 10
skinparam wrapWidth 220


legend top left
  |<#Wheat>| **Pull request** |
  Workflows run on **PR** events and deploy to **staging**: Both the SWA
  and Function App have a **staging** slot. Reviewers validate here.

  |<#LightGreen>| **Production** |
  After approval and merge to **main**, workflows deploy to **production**
  (SWA live site + Function App **production** slots.
end legend

actor "Real Users" as Real
actor "UAT Users (Developers, testing users etc.)" as Testing

package "GitHub" #dfd6d6 {
  rectangle "Repository\n(BlindReview)" as repo
  package "GitHub Actions" as gha {
    together {
      rectangle "SWA workflow\n(PR branch)" as wf_swa_pr #Wheat
      rectangle "Functions workflow\n(PR branch)" as wf_fn_pr #Wheat
    }
    together {
      rectangle "SWA workflow\n(push **main**)" as wf_swa_prod #LightGreen
      rectangle "Functions workflow\n(push **main**)" as wf_fn_prod #LightGreen
    }
  }
}


cloud "Microsoft Azure" #F5F9FF {
  frame "Staging (PR deployments)" #FFFAF0 {
    rectangle "Static Web App\n (Staging Slot)" as swa_st #Wheat
    rectangle "Function App \n(Staging Slot)" as fn_st #Wheat
  }

  frame "Production (after merge)" #F0FFF0 {
    rectangle "Static Web App\n (Production Slot)" as swa_prod #LightGreen
    rectangle "Function App \n(Production Slot)" as fn_prod #LightGreen
  }
}

Real --> swa_prod 

Testing ---> swa_st 
Real ---> fn_prod 
Testing --> fn_st 

repo --> wf_swa_pr : **PR** opened \n (target **main**)
repo --> wf_fn_pr : **PR** opened \n (target **main**)

wf_swa_pr ---> swa_st 
wf_fn_pr ---> fn_st 

repo --> wf_swa_prod : **push** **main**\n(after PR merged)
repo --> wf_fn_prod : **push** **main**\n(after PR merged)

wf_swa_prod "If approved\n after staging" --> swa_prod
wf_fn_prod "If approved\n after staging" --> fn_prod 

@enduml
